{"word":"G175 - ἄκαρπος - ákarpos - ak'-ar-pos - Without fruit","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄκαρπος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ákarpos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ak'-ar-pos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Without fruit</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பலனற்ற, பயனற்ற, கனியற்ற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"without fruit, barren"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G2590 - καρπός - karpós - kar-pos'/2590\">G2590</a>; <i>barren</i> (literally or figuratively): - without fruit, unfruitful.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G175/175\">G175</a>, <a href=\"#/G2590/2590\">G2590</a>, <a href=\"#/G2591/2591\">G2591</a>, <a href=\"#/G2592/2592\">G2592</a>, <a href=\"#/G2593/2593\">G2593</a>"}]}